# Nomi Plugin: Python Rewrite Roadmap

## Implementation Strategy
- Modular design aligned with AGENTS.md phases
- Uses `argparse` for command parsing
- Supports all existing Nomi/AI CLI verbs with arguments

### Example Command
```bash
python main.py room create "Group Chat" --nomi-uuids uuid1 uuid2
```

Integrate Nomi AI agents into your OpenClaw workflows with full REST API support.

## Installation
```bash
# Create structure
mkdir -p ~/.openclaw/skills/skill_nomi/scripts

# Install dependencies
apt-get install -y bash jq curl

# Setup credentials
export NOMI_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
export PATH="$HOME/.openclaw/skills/skill_nomi/scripts:$PATH"
```

## Core Features
- Nomi list management
- Direct 1-on-1 messaging
- Group room communication
- Avatar retrieval
- Command syntax mirroring OpenClaw standards
